data.description: Gorgeous 2 Story Home w/Swimming Pool/Spa on a Large Corner Lot in the Prestigious CHAMPION FOREST! Grand 2 Story Entry with Slate Tile Flooring, invites you into this Classy Sleek home. Freshly Painted Throughout, NEW Pool Equip, Upgrades Galore, Huge Island Kitchen w/Granite Countertops, Travertine Backsplash, Integrated Fridge, High End Chandeliers, Custom Built-ins Throughout, Travertine Floors, Hardwood Floors, Flexible Study w/Fire Place & Built ins, Formal Dining w/Swinging door to Kitchen, Triple Crown Moldings, LG Master Bedroom has a Lighted Coffered Ceiling, Separate Pool Access Door, Remodeled En-suite, Garden Jetted Tub & Separate Tiled Shower, His & Her Separate Vanities & Walk in Closet w/Hidden Closet behind shelves. Huge Game Room/Media Room UP w/Oversized Secondary Bedrooms along with 2 Full Baths, NEW HVAC System, New Water Heater, Covered Back Patio, Outdoor Kitchen, Lush Landscaping, Acclaimed Klein ISD & Close to Vintage Park!
